b24664e491f09e03276ebacf","tid":2394101,"uid":332758,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:30:23.000Z","msg":"最痛可以痛到痾嘔 漂冷汗 扯頭髮 滅自己咬自己 講唔到野 用晒全身力爭扎扭曲 休克<br />\n心情係厭惡無助 諗緊幾撚時完 到時點生仔 收縮夠未dllm..然後無念無想<br />\n<br />\n男友 唔可以置身事外<br />\n坐係床邊睇下佢有咩需要<br />\n一般煲定熱水比佢飲, 幫佢敷肚(電熱墊好過水袋, 因為唔洗換水)<br />\n熱薑茶好有用(愈辣愈好) 一飲血塊就出到黎 成身暖晒<br />\n止痛蘗要d時間先有效 超痛先食 唔係會慣左<br />\n<br />\n平日就同佢做多啲運動 留意下佢飲食啦 加油24孝男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94b0f9cbcee69653e3b0e715e6152c4534cfe6b","tid":2394101,"uid":370165,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:43:40.000Z","msg":"如果係我 我會想我另一半攬住我 搓吓個肚<br />\n不過個個唔同啦 <br />\n有啲女仔會好忟憎 我就會好sad少少嘢都想喊<br />\n如果你女朋友好忟憎唔建議你攬佢 可能佢會仲忟<br />\n紅棗水記得嚟完m先沖"},{"pid":"9301f88b7d467e8add3af900ad3d386a55884b33","tid":2394101,"uid":388655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:46:27.000Z","msg":"想你呵返我 氹我多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔舒服幾日痛到個人好唔開心 你唔好嫌煩陪下我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bad8ec4ae0a06e40acb5e37daa85bfa541ed5c","tid":2394101,"uid":162558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"26cd14343931d14c2d710af725218086aa9ed4b6","tid":2394101,"uid":27969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ba8b3890c74a0c9d16fbdc3f9a6047890ec89094","tid":2394101,"uid":130456,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"620ffd293ba517ce949c30f3299d126e8aa97d44","tid":2394101,"uid":27969,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:20:28.000Z","msg":"黎M前幾日中出好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />安全過黎完M"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:24:46.000Z","msg":"岩岩黎完=希新卵子<br />\n就黎m=更安全<br />\n條女仲會特別想要特別淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:26:47.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/as